extend /default

block content

  #app
    .prose
      h1 Welcome to Learn Tiger
    .grid  
      .grid__item.one-whole.desktop-two-thirds
        .prose
          p This is a site I set up to help my daugter Martha with her homework.
          p For now it just has a  
            a(href='/spellings') spellings test game
            |, but I'm in the process of adding a game to test number bonds.

          h2 Browser Support
          p This is personal site and it only works on very new browsers. Chrome, 
            | Safari, Mobile Safari iOS 7+. If you’ve not already, you should 
            a(href='http://www.google.com/chrome/') download Chrome for free.

          h2 Useful Learning Resources

          p Martha is learning about doubling, and halving and in this weeks
            | homework there was a link to the 
            a(href='http://www.topmarks.co.uk/maths-games/hit-the-button') Hit the Button 
            | game on the Topmarks website.
          p 
            a(href='http://www.topmarks.co.uk/maths-games/5-7-years/counting') Topmarks 
            | also has a ton of other games for learning maths and english for all 
            | age groups.

      .grid__item.one-whole.desktop-one-third
        .prose
          h2 Current Homework
          h3 Spellings
          p 
            a(href='/spellings/2015-09-21') “kn...” Monday 21 September 2015
          h3 Conkers - Harvest Festival Song
          p I'm think this is the version they are meant to learn.
          iframe(width='100%', height='200', src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/zatImJzgyZQ', frameborder='0', allowfullscreen)
          h3 Number Bonds - 12
          pre
            - for (i = 0; i <= 12; i++)
              - var asc = i, desc = 12 - i
              | #{asc < 10 ? ' ' + asc : asc} + #{desc < 10 ? ' ' + desc : desc} = 12 <br />
        
        

